data.description:
SOLAR PANELS INCLUDED

ASK ABOUT THE $5000 SELLER CONTRIBUTON TO CLOSING COSTS

Indulge in luxury with this exceptional two-story residence boasting not only the modern elegance of granite countertops and refrigerated air but also the added benefit of fully PAID OFF SOLAR PANELS. Revel in the beauty of an open-concept layout, seamlessly connecting living spaces, and discover the convenience of a loft upstairs, offering versatile usage to suit your needs. Enjoy the tranquility of spacious rooms and relish the privacy of no backdoor neighbors, providing a retreat-like atmosphere. Entertain in style with an outdoor kitchen and pergola, creating a captivating backdrop for gatherings and celebrations. The backyard oasis is adorned with lush turf, offering a perfect blend of aesthetics and low-maintenance living. Enjoy the convenience of security system prewire already in place. Dont miss your opportunity to secure a great home in the sought after Enchanted Hills community, schedule your showing today!
